title: Ground News - “Massive underdog” triumphs: The best minutes of darts life aren't enough
text:
Summary by N-tv.de Florian Hempel experienced the best minutes of his darts life so far within a week, but the German darts professional can only benefit from them once. In round three, the World Cup against Stephen Bunting is over. He now declares himself a “massive underdog.” Share menu More
